*Možda* ću novi grad posetiti za vikend. (Maybe I will visit the new city for the weekend.)

*Možda* ću učiti sutra. (Maybe I will study tomorrow.)

Ne znam *možda* li mogu da pomognem. (I don't know maybe I can help.)

*Možda* će biti lepog vremena sutra. (Maybe it will be nice weather tomorrow.)

*Možda* ću negde otići u subotu. (Maybe I will go somewhere on Saturday.)